title: The Agent In Estonia
description: One of our FSociety agents was undercover in Estonia in 2017. We haven't heard from him since, and we thought he was KIA. However, we've recently recieved intel about a Gitlab account created with their name, as well as a private repo called 'secret-file'. Clearly the agent is trying to give us some information, but what is it?
author: Clayton Smith and Forest Anderson
